frames.caption: A woman clings desperately to the side of a steep cliff, her face showing fear and determination. Below her, a rushing river flows through a narrow gorge, adding to the perilous nature of her climb.
frames.description: The scene depicts a tense moment of rock climbing in a dramatic natural setting. The woman is suspended on a cliff face, with a turbulent river below, highlighting the danger and intensity of the situation.

frames.caption: A climber clings desperately to a sheer rock face, high above a turbulent river gorge. Her expression is one of fear and determination as she navigates the perilous climb. The misty atmosphere and rugged terrain emphasize the danger of the situation.
frames.description: The scene depicts a climber in a precarious position on a steep rock face, with a deep gorge and rushing river below. The setting is dramatic and tense, highlighting the climber's struggle and the natural beauty of the environment.
